Description: Fragments of papyrus with 10 lines of Demotic text, in black and red ink on recto. Part of the Book of the Temple, same ms as Vienna Aeg 6339 + 8447 + 8449; P. Carlsberg 315; P. Berlin 14946; unnumbered fragments in Louvre.
Curator's comments: To be published by Joachim Friedrich Quack (Heidelberg)
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380690) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380690)
